# Keyboard shortcuts
# Command                     # Shortcut / command        # Plugin
split windows                 :vsplit <filename>          -
split windows (read-only)     :sview <filename>           -
edit another file             :e filename                 -
open buffer                   :b <buffer-number>          -
list buffers                  :ls                         -
switch between windows        CTRL + ww                   -
switch to window              CTRL + arrow                -
full path file search         CTRL + p                    ctrlp.vim
multiple cursors              CTRL + n                    vim-multiple-cursors

# Visual Mode
indent                        > 
unindent                      <
multi line comment            gc                          tcomment_vim
switch case                   ~

